Package view

Class SceneController

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
view.SceneController
public class SceneController extends javafx.application.Application
This class is the controller of the frame switcher of the application. It is the controller that check the uniqueness of the pseudo. It is the controller that switch between the different frames of the application.
